---
// Homepage company promise (Step 7, Brief §6.3). Serif quote + verbatim body paragraph.
// Copy is VERBATIM, em dashes included.
import Section from '../ui/Section.astro';
import PullQuote from '../ui/PullQuote.astro';
---

<Section bg="default" width="narrow" space="lg">
  <PullQuote class="nx-promise__quote">
    Nigeria's development challenges are rarely solved by a single capability. We built Northaxis to
    be the firm that stays — across procurement, technology, and energy — delivering both the
    equipment and the strategic advice until the work is done.
  </PullQuote>
  <p class="nx-promise__body">
    Founded in Benin City, Northaxis Integrated Services Limited is a CAC-registered integrated
    solutions firm. We work with state governments, federal agencies, development finance
    institutions, and private sector clients who need a reliable, locally rooted partner with the
    range and expertise to see complex projects through — from supply to strategy.
  </p>
</Section>

<style>
  .nx-promise__body {
    margin: 1.75rem 0 0;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-grey);
  }
</style>
